# Intern 1: Strict Types

- Do not use `any`.
- Replace weak shapes like `Record<string, number>` with explicit nested interfaces.
- Model `astMetrics` and `aiSmells` at every level the mock data exposes.
- Export reusable types from `src/lib/repo-analysis.types.ts`.
- Keep component props and helper signatures aligned with the exported types.
